<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema525_05_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema525_su_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema525_04_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">정육면체의 전개도를 찾아봅시다.
        </h2>
      </section>
        
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">정육면체의 전개도가 될 수 있는 것을 예상해 보세요.</h3> 
          
          <div class="contents_img">
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA525_04_SU/0004_contents1.png" alt="정육면체의 전개도 이미지"/>
            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b" lang="y">가</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b" lang="y">나</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b" lang="y">다</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b" lang="y">라</span></button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">직접 접어서 정육면체의 전개도가 될 수 있는 것을 모두 찾아 기호를 찾아 보세요.</h3> 
          
          <div class="contents_img">
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA525_04_SU/0004_contents1.png" alt="정육면체의 전개도 이미지"/>
            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b" lang="y">가</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b" lang="y">나</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="false"><span class="f24b" lang="y">다</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b" lang="y">라</span></button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_3">
          <h3 lang="y">정육면체의 전개도가 될 수 없는 것을 찾아 기호를 쓰고, 그 이유를 이야기해 보세요.</h3> 

          <div class="wrap">
            <div class="contents_img">
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA525_04_SU/0004_contents1.png" alt="정육면체의 전개도 이미지"/>
              <div class="boolean_wrap">
                <button data-answer-single="false"><span class="f24b" lang="y">가</span></button>
                <button data-answer-single="false"><span class="f24b" lang="y">나</span></button>
                <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b" lang="y">다</span></button>
                <button data-answer-single="false"><span class="f24b" lang="y">라</span></button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="leftside input_area">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
                  <p lang="y">접었을 때 겹치는 두 면이 있습니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <!-- <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button> -->
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
